column5: Pictures a little tiny, but looks like a nice fish. WTG!!
Which little lake.  I'm assuming Peterbouough area..  Nice fish to eh!
Probably Little Lake up by Gloucester pool. Nice fish.  Looks like a barracuda. lol
Wow, pretty skinny ski.  Congrats on the catch!  Joey
Little Lake muskies have a tendancy to be on the thin side, they should bulk up by feeding on the greenwing specks and rainbows that get released through the canal below the liftlocks each year
